description:
This plugin for KeePass 2.x can import TXT files that were exported by CodeWallet 3.

Note that this importer is specifically for CodeWallet 3 files.

KeePass 2.x already includes an importer for CodeWallet 6 files.
summary: Plugin for KeePass 2.x to import TXT files that were exported by CodeWallet 3
author: Sebastian Baumhekel
